title: Rent with right to purchase, you pick the house!
posting_body: ['rent period: monthly', 'Looking for a home to rent in the Puyallup area?', 'I can help!', 'In order to qualify for the Rent To Own Program:', '• You must have at least $85,000 in Combined Gross Household Income', '•', 'A minimum FICO score of 620', '• No evictions in the past 3 years', '• Takes 5-6 weeks from start to finish', 'We work with previous bankruptcies, foreclosures and short sales!', 'There is a 1 time $75 application fee, which is good for the whole household, and for any of our qualifying houses!', 'You must be pre-approved to view any available properties.', 'Pet Friendly!', 'Up to 3 cats/dogs OKAY!', '(Due to extreme insurance liability, we cannot allow Dobermans, Pitbulls, Rottweilers or Mastiffs)', 'Contact me today for more information and details about the program!', 'Amanda Marques', 'Coldwell Banker Bain', "The home in the picture is an example of what you could get, it's not this home in particular."]
